Mission.Title: C7M10sanitized final
Mission.Comments:
CAMPAIGN 7: NEOFEUDAL SANDLORDS MISSION 10: TÜRKMAXXED BRICK DEALFLOW
Last week, we defended a massive ground assault on our foothold in Incirlik, supported by bombers, SEAD flights, and strikers.
With our place in the region beyond negotiation, we're taking a contract of our own on the side to help absorb our costs.
This week, we've set up a sale of 5,000lbs of synthcoke in exchange for 20,000lbs of gold bullion. The agreement is to fly in the dope by cargo aircraft, drop parachute crates to their agents on the ground, then the buyer's dump trucks filled with bullion will drop their cargo to be slung back to the FARP.
One problem is we don't have any synthcoke to sell, so we're going to drop 12 crates of empty churu tubes and then bomb the dealsite. Our helos will drop ground teams to sweep the zone and shoot their way to the gold, then egress.
We're having some problems renewing our blanket casualty and liability insurance policy and instead of kidnapping our agent's pets, we're going to drop 4,000lbs of bullion into her backyard on the way back to the FARP.
Company Objective: Pretend to sell a turkish nationalist militia 12 crates full of synthcoke, obtain the payment, return to the FARP.
Company Secondary Objective: Deliver 4,000lbs of gold bullion to our insurance agent's backyard.
Weather: Clear, 23degC, light wind Mission Local Time: 1608
